title: How I Maintain 100lbs Down
itunes:title: How I Maintain 100lbs Down
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

Today we talk about maintenance. I get asked about this all the time! "What's different about maintenance Corinne?" and "What do I do now that I've lost all my weight?"

Listen in. We talk about developing the belief that you can keep your weight off. We also talk some more about our weight loss and the hiccups we had in our thinking as we lost the weight and learned to keep it off.
